quikscript-a simscript- like language for the g-.wquikscript is a simulation language based onsimscript and programmed entirely in an algebraic language, -gate.  the quikscript language, its internalimplementation, and major differences between quikscript and simscript are presented.  this paper isnot a programming guide to the language, but rather an attempt to present its flavor.  a brief description ofsimscript is included, as is a sufficient description of -gate to render this material understandableto the reader familiar with algebraic languages.cacm june, tonge, f. m.keller, p.newell, a.ca jb march ,   : pm